data.description: This 4Bd 3.5 bath property features: a finished bonus room; 2 car garage; natural lighting; security system; and storage. Upon entry, is a thoughtful layout including cathedral style ceilings across the living room and formal dining area. Luxury extends into the kitchen including: granite countertops w/ crown molding; double oven; stainless steel appliances; and a cozy eat-in nook. Meeting the kitchen is an additional family space w/tray ceilings that leads to the outdoor covered patio and BBQ area. The tranquil owner's suite features access to the outback patio, a sitting area w/ gas fireplace, as well as the ensuite features a walk-in, tiled shower and full jetted bathtub w/ countertop storage, double sinks, & a walk-in closet with shelving. The secondary bedrooms are equally spacious, sharing a jack and jill concept full bath. Upstairs is a finished bonus area w/ additional flex space, two skylights, a closet and attic storage. This home is a luxury masterpiece of design & comfort.
